// Integral number overflow
1234567890123456789
1E25

// An integral number with incorrect use of underscore
1__3
_3 // This is actually valid, prefix _
3_

// An integral number with an invalid base
1#0
37#A

// An integral number with a digit outside the base
2#103
15#10FFE

